description: Beautiful City Point penthouse with four deeded garage parking spaces (two single and one tandem) and direct elevator access. The main level features an open kitchen with custom inset cabinetry, a Sub-Zero refrigerator, a Wolf five-burner range, double Wolf ovens, a Jenn-Air microwave drawer, Asko dishwasher, and oversized Quartzite slab island. A built-in bar with refrigerated drawers, a powder room, and a den/3rd bedroom complete this level. The living room features a gas fireplace, flanked by custom-built-in shelving. The upper level features a lounge with a wet bar and a wine/beverage refrigerator, opening to a private roof deck with expansive views and natural gas hookups. The lower level includes two bedrooms, two full baths, and a laundry closet. The primary suite features an ensuite bath with a steam shower and a custom walk-in closet. In-unit laundry, new HVAC, California closet systems, an oversized storage locker, and abundant garage storage space complete this offering.

exclusions: Tv's Are Excluded From The Sale.
